§7§oApplied Energistics is a high-capability logistics mod.

Alone, it can manage a large part of your base, including item storage, autocrafting, and managing passive automations externally.

Expect to build a massive AE2 network, and likely a ton of small ones too!

The following quests show all tools available in this complex but powerful mod!
